<br>
&quot;Maybe while you're camping uber mob_01 somewhere you should take a look at the DPS of the rogues and monks on your raid... and compare that to the DPS of your wizards and mages. Then come back and tell me that a 20% boost to caster damage output is going to &quot;completely unbalance&quot; the game.&quot;<br>
<br>
Raid last night.  Every SINGLE loot announcement came from the caster group.  This is pretty much the norm in any luclin encounter.  I don't have hard parsing numbers, but I do have that little bit of trivia.<br>
<br>
There are two types of balance -- class vs. class, and player versus enemy.  When Zaz says that a 20% boost in caster damage is going to completely unbalance the game, she's not talking about how it stacks casters compared to other classes.  She's talking about the drastic decrease in the difficulty of raid encounters.<br>
<br>
